anime.my_comments: This anime is like eating. It doesn't mean that if a thing is edible, you should put it inside your mouth. It's the same for this show. But, like food, I can't help but admire the production and great budgeting they made with the animation- it has the plating of a Michelin star but unfortunately, taste horribly. Same with the show, everything is so bad ngl though it has the right mix to get me addicted on it. Just can't help that the production is really great especially that ED. That's a banger.
